1
00:00:13,300 --> 00:00:16,436
♪The greedy heart shuttles, unrelenting♪

2
00:00:16,436 --> 00:00:19,668
♪The lonely sadness feels no sin♪

3
00:00:19,924 --> 00:00:23,284
♪Fearing no false names
being forced upon me♪

4
00:00:23,564 --> 00:00:29,012
♪Who is sneaking in spite
as night falls♪

5
00:00:32,564 --> 00:00:35,764
♪Quietly enjoying the dark world♪

6
00:00:35,956 --> 00:00:39,164
♪I only look forward to dawn's beauty♪

7
00:00:39,412 --> 00:00:42,548
♪The sun's warmth burns away guilt♪

8
00:00:42,676 --> 00:00:45,940
♪Killing the innocence
that redeems love♪

9
00:00:53,492 --> 00:00:55,040
=Marry to the Enemy of My Enemy=

10
00:00:55,040 --> 00:00:57,300
=Episode 24=

11
00:00:57,971 --> 00:01:00,800
(One Month Later)

12
00:01:30,480 --> 00:01:32,359
The moment you had Meng Yizhe
work with you

13
00:01:33,079 --> 00:01:35,040
to lie to me that your surgery failed,

14
00:01:35,560 --> 00:01:37,359
my heartbeat and breathing stopped.

15
00:01:38,319 --> 00:01:40,159
I didn't know
what I would do without you.

16
00:01:47,079 --> 00:01:47,879
Were you scared?

17
00:01:48,719 --> 00:01:51,120
Now you know
what it feels like to be lied to.

18
00:01:53,239 --> 00:01:54,040
I know now.

19
00:01:57,560 --> 00:01:58,359
I'm sorry.

20
00:01:58,840 --> 00:02:00,200
How did you know I'd be here?

21
00:02:01,519 --> 00:02:02,959
Today is Mom's birthday.

22
00:02:03,799 --> 00:02:04,799
You told me before

23
00:02:05,439 --> 00:02:07,040
Mom liked to bring you here the most.

24
00:02:13,680 --> 00:02:15,800
If Mom saw me now,

25
00:02:16,080 --> 00:02:18,240
would she think I'm happy?

26
00:02:21,960 --> 00:02:24,599
Mom, I'm Zhong Xinyang.

27
00:02:26,520 --> 00:02:27,719
I am Xia Nuan's husband.

28
00:02:30,120 --> 00:02:31,120
I promise you,

29
00:02:31,960 --> 00:02:33,319
with me by Nuan's side,

30
00:02:34,039 --> 00:02:36,919
she will surely be healthy and happy.

31
00:02:39,124 --> 00:02:47,172
♪Cause' I see sparks fly
whenever you smile♪

32
00:02:49,680 --> 00:02:50,479
(Nuan,)

33
00:02:51,080 --> 00:02:52,719
(from now on, Zhongxia)

34
00:02:53,000 --> 00:02:54,240
(is yours again.)

35
00:02:54,719 --> 00:02:56,080
(Don't think about being lazy.)

36
00:02:57,080 --> 00:02:58,319
(As for me,)

37
00:02:59,159 --> 00:03:00,199
(although Ji Yiran didn't)

38
00:03:00,199 --> 00:03:01,599
(report my illegal detention,)

39
00:03:02,080 --> 00:03:03,319
(I'll turn myself in)

40
00:03:03,800 --> 00:03:05,039
(to accept my punishment.)

41
00:03:06,039 --> 00:03:07,439
(I will also undergo treatment)

42
00:03:07,639 --> 00:03:09,439
(to restart my surgical career.)

43
00:03:10,759 --> 00:03:12,280
(You were right.)

44
00:03:13,000 --> 00:03:14,560
(The former Dr. Meng)

45
00:03:15,039 --> 00:03:16,000
(should be back.)

46
00:03:16,879 --> 00:03:17,680
Nuan.

47
00:03:48,639 --> 00:03:49,120
Your coffee.

48
00:03:49,879 --> 00:03:50,479
Thank you.

49
00:03:51,240 --> 00:03:52,064
- Baby.
- Yes?

50
00:03:52,319 --> 00:03:53,680
Which cake do you want to eat?

51
00:03:54,240 --> 00:03:55,800
I want to eat...

52
00:03:56,199 --> 00:03:57,360
- Dark chocolate cake.
- Strawberry cake?

53
00:03:59,400 --> 00:04:00,360
- Mango cake?
- Tiramisu.

54
00:04:02,360 --> 00:04:03,400
- Cream cake?
- Black forest cake.

55
00:04:04,520 --> 00:04:07,520
Baby, I don't want a child
with a dark complexion.

56
00:04:08,240 --> 00:04:09,199
No black coffee anymore.

57
00:04:14,360 --> 00:04:16,279
(Room Card Key)
The room card is with me.

58
00:04:22,399 --> 00:04:23,360
Let me out.

59
00:04:24,639 --> 00:04:25,680
Let me out!

60
00:04:29,759 --> 00:04:31,519
I'm not sick. Let me out.

61
00:04:32,959 --> 00:04:35,160
Is anyone there?

62
00:04:36,680 --> 00:04:38,319
You'll all die a terrible death.

63
00:04:38,680 --> 00:04:40,160
A terrible death.

64
00:04:41,279 --> 00:04:43,040
Zhongxia is going public.

65
00:04:43,160 --> 00:04:44,920
You. You.

66
00:04:45,279 --> 00:04:47,079
Die a terrible death!

67
00:04:47,600 --> 00:04:48,399
You...

68
00:04:51,560 --> 00:04:53,439
It's gone. I've eaten it.

69
00:04:53,439 --> 00:04:55,120
The Xia family is nothing.

70
00:04:55,319 --> 00:04:56,600
Die a terrible death.

71
00:05:10,439 --> 00:05:12,680
I hate your condescending attitude

72
00:05:12,680 --> 00:05:13,959
and arrogant demeanor the most.

73
00:05:13,959 --> 00:05:15,560
You are so like your mom.

74
00:05:21,040 --> 00:05:21,959
What a pity.

75
00:05:22,920 --> 00:05:26,759
You didn't see your mom
crying and kneeling before she died,

76
00:05:26,759 --> 00:05:28,600
begging me to spare you.

77
00:05:28,959 --> 00:05:31,040
What makes people like you so special?

78
00:05:31,040 --> 00:05:32,839
You were simply born
into a better family.

79
00:05:33,079 --> 00:05:33,959
Ji Yantao,

80
00:05:34,600 --> 00:05:36,160
do you still remember

81
00:05:36,160 --> 00:05:37,639
the energy stone Ji Yiran gave you?

82
00:05:38,480 --> 00:05:39,279
What do you mean?

83
00:05:43,959 --> 00:05:46,480
That thing has a kind
of long-term radiation.

84
00:05:47,120 --> 00:05:49,560
Long-term close contact
can cause cancer.

85
00:05:50,639 --> 00:05:52,000
Nonsense.

86
00:05:54,360 --> 00:05:56,120
You use family ties as a weapon.

87
00:05:56,120 --> 00:05:57,959
Have you thought about
how she would treat you?

88
00:05:59,639 --> 00:06:00,879
(It's an energy stone.)

89
00:06:01,399 --> 00:06:02,879
Bring it with you.

90
00:06:03,120 --> 00:06:04,439
It's good for your health.

91
00:06:04,959 --> 00:06:08,439
Yiran, you're really a big girl now.

92
00:06:11,360 --> 00:06:14,000
Enjoy your last moments well.

93
00:06:55,759 --> 00:06:56,759
I'm going to work.

94
00:06:57,160 --> 00:06:57,959
I'll see you off.

95
00:06:58,160 --> 00:06:59,399
No need. I can go by myself...

96
00:07:00,079 --> 00:07:00,879
I...

97
00:07:02,160 --> 00:07:02,959
What are you doing?

98
00:07:08,959 --> 00:07:10,839
You're either in meetings
or working all day,

99
00:07:10,839 --> 00:07:12,600
leaving me alone in an empty house.

100
00:07:12,920 --> 00:07:14,279
Can't you spend some time with me?

101
00:07:14,519 --> 00:07:16,399
Zhongxia is about to go public.

102
00:07:16,800 --> 00:07:19,759
And today's meeting is quite important.

103
00:07:22,360 --> 00:07:23,360
But today,

104
00:07:23,680 --> 00:07:25,160
you have something more important.

105
00:07:28,240 --> 00:07:30,160
Today is Crazy Thursday.

106
00:07:38,932 --> 00:07:43,878
♪I always needed time to on my own♪

107
00:07:45,952 --> 00:07:50,272
♪Never thought I'd need someone
when I cry♪

108
00:07:52,768 --> 00:07:55,136
♪You take me to the sky♪

109
00:07:55,731 --> 00:07:58,835
♪And you take away the pain♪

110
00:07:59,232 --> 00:08:06,559
♪Cause' I see sparks fly
whenever you smile♪

111
00:08:07,796 --> 00:08:11,350
♪You are so beautiful to me♪

112
00:08:13,014 --> 00:08:14,454
♪Can you see♪

113
00:08:14,698 --> 00:08:16,982
♪You are so beautiful♪

114
00:08:17,654 --> 00:08:18,774
♪To me♪

115
00:08:20,768 --> 00:08:22,079
♪To me♪

116
00:08:32,799 --> 00:08:34,360
Nuan, could you wait for us for a bit?

117
00:08:34,759 --> 00:08:36,639
(Five Years Later)
You turned off my alarm again.

118
00:08:36,639 --> 00:08:38,120
It's because the kids need more rest

119
00:08:38,120 --> 00:08:39,320
to grow properly.

120
00:08:39,559 --> 00:08:40,919
The parent-child event is at 3 PM.

121
00:08:40,919 --> 00:08:41,519
Don't forget.

122
00:08:42,000 --> 00:08:43,200
What is a parent-child event?

123
00:08:43,480 --> 00:08:44,879
Wait. It's our event.

124
00:08:45,200 --> 00:08:46,440
I scheduled with you last week.

125
00:08:46,440 --> 00:08:47,440
Did you forget again?

126
00:08:49,200 --> 00:08:50,799
3 PM, got it.

127
00:08:54,279 --> 00:08:56,120
She abandons us again.

128
00:08:56,759 --> 00:08:57,919
Stop the nonsense.

129
00:08:57,919 --> 00:08:58,919
I always want you.

130
00:09:00,600 --> 00:09:01,320
Let me kiss you.

131
00:09:01,320 --> 00:09:02,000
No.

132
00:09:02,399 --> 00:09:03,120
Let's go.

133
00:09:04,000 --> 00:09:05,879
We don't let her kiss us, okay?
Hurry up.

134
00:09:06,919 --> 00:09:07,759
Let's go.

135
00:09:08,279 --> 00:09:09,679
Be careful, Zhong Xinyang.

136
00:09:09,679 --> 00:09:10,279
Let's go.

137
00:09:10,279 --> 00:09:11,200
Let's go.

138
00:09:11,440 --> 00:09:12,240
Slow down.

139
00:09:13,587 --> 00:09:16,864
♪Butterflies quietly enter the sight♪

140
00:09:17,460 --> 00:09:18,496
♪Falling in love♪

141
00:09:18,656 --> 00:09:20,864
♪There is no time difference in love♪

142
00:09:21,268 --> 00:09:23,776
♪No need to question its authenticity♪

143
00:09:23,817 --> 00:09:26,096
♪Can you be like this♪

144
00:09:26,406 --> 00:09:28,896
♪And stay with me forever?♪

145
00:09:29,760 --> 00:09:32,192
♪It's so dramatic♪

146
00:09:32,468 --> 00:09:34,112
♪Like two fools♪

147
00:09:34,112 --> 00:09:35,968
♪Kissing♪

148
00:09:36,448 --> 00:09:41,248
♪Just dream, laugh, and love♪

149
00:09:49,620 --> 00:09:50,590
(Ji Yantao, Ji Yiran, Meng Yizhe,
Zha Meng, Ao Tu, and Ms. Wang)

150
00:09:50,590 --> 00:09:51,950
(all were justly tried by the law.
Before the law, everyone is equal.)

151
00:09:51,950 --> 00:09:53,074
(This drama is a warning to the world:
illegal doings will be punished by law.)

152
00:09:53,299 --> 00:09:54,829
(Xia Nuan established a special fund
for kidney diseases in Xia Li's name,)

153
00:09:54,829 --> 00:09:56,416
(providing financial help for patients
and bringing them hope.)

154
00:09:56,416 --> 00:09:59,328
(The End)

155
00:10:07,443 --> 00:10:11,379
♪You said you wanted
to be my guardian angel♪

156
00:10:11,379 --> 00:10:15,091
♪In wind and rain,
even if with broken wings♪

157
00:10:15,091 --> 00:10:20,339
♪It wouldn't stop you from loving me♪

158
00:10:22,163 --> 00:10:26,483
♪I wanted to thank you
for giving me courage♪

159
00:10:26,483 --> 00:10:30,131
♪Carry me out of this trouble and soar♪

160
00:10:30,131 --> 00:10:36,499
♪But when I turn around,
you've already left♪

161
00:10:37,459 --> 00:10:41,171
♪Why should I love you
without hesitation♪

162
00:10:41,171 --> 00:10:44,723
♪Falling from paradise
all the way to the ruins♪

163
00:10:45,267 --> 00:10:48,723
♪In your net called love♪

164
00:10:48,723 --> 00:10:51,923
♪Why am I just a pawn at your whim♪

165
00:10:52,467 --> 00:10:55,987
♪Why should I love you
without hesitation♪

166
00:10:56,147 --> 00:11:00,147
♪In exchange for the complete defeat♪

167
00:11:00,147 --> 00:11:05,747
♪Don't you have a bit of mercy♪
